1. *Stignemo* do kuće za sat vremena. (We will arrive at home in an hour.)
2. Oni će najverovatnije *stignuti* pre nas. (They will most likely arrive before us.)
3. Želim da *stignemo* što pre. (I want us to arrive as soon as possible.)
4. Nismo se uspeli *stići* u vreme. (We didn't manage to arrive on time.)
5. *Stigli* su da nas podsete. (They arrived to remind us.)